    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and meticulously cared for. You won't find a single blemish on it! It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
