      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal engineering. The S54 inline-six features a high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear torque curve and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, featuring a reinforced subframe and a bulletproofed valvetrain. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M differential lock. The chassis retains its factory rigidity with pristine bushings and an untouched suspension geometry. Cosmetically, the finish exhibits factory-spec depth with zero oxidation, and the interior bolsters show no signs of compression or wear. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
